<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>18Day - Challenge Accepted!</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #4361EE;
      --primary-dark: #3A0CA3;
      --accent: #F72585;
      --light: #F8F9FA;
      --dark: #212529;
      --success: #4CC9F0;
      --gray: #6C757D;
    }
    
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--dark);
      background-color: #f4f5f7;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .logo h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    .logo p {
      color: var(--gray);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    
    .card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .habit-box {
      background-color: var(--light);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--dark);
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .success-badge {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      background-color: var(--success);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 40px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(76, 201, 240, 0.3);
    }
    
    .day-progress {
      display: flex;
      margin: 25px 0;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    
    .day {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background-color: #E9ECEF;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--dark);
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .day.critical {
      background-color: var(--accent);
      color: white;
    }
    
    .day.active {
      background-color: var(--primary);
      color: white;
    }
    
    .day:after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      height: 2px;
      background-color: #E9ECEF;
      width: 100%;
      left: 100%;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      z-index: -1;
    }
    
    .day:last-child:after {
      display: none;
    }
    
    .info-card {
      background-color: var(--light);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--success);
    }
    
    .info-card h3 {
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <h1>18Day</h1>
      <p>The Habit Launchpad</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card">
      <div class="success-badge">âœ“</div>
      
      <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">You're on your way!</h2>
      
      <p><strong><%= friendEmail %></strong> has accepted your 18-day habit challenge:</p>
      
      <div class="habit-box">
        <%= habitDescription %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="day-progress">
        <div class="day active">1</div>
        <div class="day critical">6</div>
        <div class="day critical">12</div>
        <div class="day critical">18</div>
        <div class="day">30</div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="info-card">
        <h3>Your 18-Day Journey Has Begun</h3>
        <p>You'll both receive daily check-in emails at 9pm. The next 18 days are critical for forming this habit into a lasting neural pathway.</p>
      </div>
      
      <p>Remember, consistency is key during these first 18 days when your brain is forming new neural connections!</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Based on habit formation research by Phillippa Lally et al., UCL</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>